{"type":"message","id":"ec190b96","parentId":"9e1a83a5","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:01:42.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a screenshot showing the output of `openclaw browser status`. Let me analyze what I see:\n\n- Profile: openclaw\n- Status: Enabled but not running\n- Transport: CDP on port 18800\n- Browser: unknown, detected as \"chrome\" at `/usr/bin/google-chrome-stable`\n- Color: #FF4500\n\nThe browser is not currently running. I need to tell the user to start the browser first with `openclaw browser start`, then open the URL.\n\nBut wait - I don't have exec tool access. I cannot run commands on the user's machine. I can only guide them to do it themselves.\n\nLet me reply clearly: the browser is configured and ready, but not running. They need to start it first."},{"type":"text","text":"看到截图了！浏览器已经配置好（检测到 Chrome 在 `/usr/bin/google-chrome-stable`），但目前**没有运行**。\n\n**接下来两步：**\n\n**第一步：启动浏览器**\n在新终端运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw browser start\n```\n\n**第二步：打开 echotik.live**\n```bash\nopenclaw browser open https://echotik.live/\n```\n\n或者启动后直接告诉我\"浏览器已启动\"，我就可以通过内置的 `browser` 工具来帮你操作页面（截图、点击、填表等）。\n\n---\n\n启动后把结果截图发给我看看～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776340892446,"responseId":"0630029cf465e223f99010940164230b"}}
