{"type":"message","id":"432bf592","parentId":"99783852","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:02:45.136Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/760a950c-6848-422d-9e28-bf0596ffc142.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/760a950c-6848-422d-9e28-bf0596ffc142.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-16 20:02:35 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b5138b36d10b0c2d55d932ffe6f8, post, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5138b36d10b0c2d55d932ffe6f8\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 20:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 Thu 2026-04-16 20:02 GMT+8] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/760a950c-6848-422d-9e28-bf0596ffc142.jpg\n开了，确定chrome不需要安装插件对吧\nDescription:\nThe image shows the **Remote debugging** settings page in Chrome DevTools (`chrome://inspect/#remote-debugging`).\n\nKey details include:\n* **Checkbox enabled:** \"Allow remote debugging for this browser instance\" is selected.\n* **Security warning:** It warns that enabling this allows external apps full control, including access to saved data and cookies.\n* **Server status:** The remote debugging server is running at `127.0.0.1:9222`.\n* **Link:** A link at the bottom points to info about \"Chrome D"}],"timestamp":1776340965119}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e9d7a83","parentId":"432bf592","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:03:02.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has enabled remote debugging in Chrome and is asking again to confirm that Chrome doesn't need any plugins installed. They're showing the chrome://inspect/#remote-debugging page which shows the remote debugging server is running at 127.0.0.1:9222.\n\nLet me confirm - OpenClaw's built-in browser tool does NOT require any Chrome plugin. It uses CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) directly. The user has already enabled remote debugging, which is good.\n\nHowever, I should note that:\n1. OpenClaw's `openclaw` profile uses its own CDP port (18800), not the 9222 port the user has open\n2. But there's also a `user` profile mode that can use the 9222 port\n\nLet me check the configuration. The user's Chrome is listening on port 9222. For OpenClaw to connect to it, we'd need to configure the `user` profile with `attachOnly: true` and the appropriate CDP URL.\n\nBut actually, looking at the docs, there are two approaches:\n1. `openclaw` managed browser - separate browser instance\n2. `user` profile - attaches to existing Chrome via Chrome DevTools MCP\n\nSince the user has already opened remote debugging on port 9222, they could use the `user` profile or the `remote` profile to attach to it.\n\nLet me clarify with the user and help them proceed. The key point is: NO Chrome plugin needed."},{"type":"text","text":"**确认：Chrome 不需要安装任何插件！** ✅\n\nOpenClaw 通过 Chrome 内置的 **CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol)** 直接控制浏览器，你已经开启的远程调试就是 CDP。\n\n---\n\n**你的 Chrome 已经在 9222 端口运行远程调试了**，接下来配置一下就能用。\n\n在你的 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加 `user` 配置：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"browser\": {\n    \"profiles\": {\n      \"user\": {\n        \"driver\": \"existing-session\",\n        \"attachOnly\": true\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n然后重启 Gateway：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后告诉我，我就能通过 `browser` 工具帮你操作 Chrome 了——打开网页、点击、填表、截图都行。\n\n---\n\n**或者更简单**：你直接保持现在的 Chrome 运行着，告诉我\"已开启远程调试\"，我来处理后续连接。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776340965163,"responseId":"063002e500731e52a89a90da4161dcab"}}
