{"type":"message","id":"b42c5436","parentId":"ac037096","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:16:02.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I successfully controlled the browser via the API! I can see the full page content of echotik.live. The browser is working through the API. Now I need to let the user know that I've successfully controlled the browser and opened echotik.live.\n\nThe exec tool is working now - I can send HTTP requests to the browser control API at port 18791. I should let the user know it's working and ask what they want me to do next on the page."},{"type":"text","text":"**成功了！🎉**\n\nChrome 已控制，echotik.live 已打开。我能看到页面上的所有内容：\n- 视频榜（美国）前10名\n- 小店榜前10名（ medicube、POP MART、MaryRuth's 等）\n- 三级类目竞争分析\n\n**你现在可以在你的 Chrome 上看到这个页面。**\n\n接下来你想做什么？比如：\n1. **点击某个链接/按钮**（告诉我目标）\n2. **截图看看你的屏幕**\n3. **导航到其他页面**（比如泰国/越南站点）\n4. **登录账号**（如果你有 echotik 账号）\n\n直接告诉我指令就行！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776341751816,"responseId":"063005f89561973f8862e7ec28471771"}}
