{"type":"message","id":"82a6d449","parentId":"2d2a4f57","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:20:08.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"截图保存在 /home/halei/.openclaw/media/browser/6936a59d-f1d0-49b5-9682-a7867cc53869.jpg。我应该发送这个图片给用户。"},{"type":"text","text":"**已成功连接你的 Chrome！** 🎉\n\nechotik.live 已打开。你现在应该也能在你的 Chrome 屏幕上看到这个页面。\n\nMEDIA:/home/halei/.openclaw/media/browser/6936a59d-f1d0-49b5-9682-a7867cc53869.jpg\n\n---\n\n接下来你想做什么？比如：\n1. **登录 echotik 账号**（告诉我账号密码）\n2. **导航到泰国/越南站点**\n3. **进入选品库/新品榜**\n4. **其他操作**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776342003605,"responseId":"063006f3d435b213bcb634bd8d961732"}}
