{"type":"message","id":"3a69b9db","parentId":"f36f52f9","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:20:47.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你现在经过我同意在调整设置哈\" - meaning \"You're now adjusting settings with my consent\" - basically they're acknowledging that I've been making config changes and they're okay with it. They're giving me permission to continue adjusting settings.\n\nLet me acknowledge this and continue. They want to use the `user` instance (their existing Chrome). The user profile is already configured. Let me ask them to restart the gateway so the new browser config takes effect, then we can proceed."},{"type":"text","text":"好的，明白了！👍\n\n目前我已经做的修改：\n1. ✅ 添加了 `exec` 和 `process` 工具到 tts agent\n2. ✅ 添加了 `browser.profiles.user` 配置\n\n现在需要你做一件事：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后我来确认 `user` 实例是否正常连接，然后我们就可以开始操作了（登录 echotik、导航到选品页面等）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776342039850,"responseId":"06300718f5f2d37f089bfe0abb6b5c43"}}
