{"type":"message","id":"ebc582b3","parentId":"6b2e83cd","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:47:01.203Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 20:46:59 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b5139eaed2c6cc2cf3c28eb370e5]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5139eaed2c6cc2cf3c28eb370e5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 20:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n之前的vibesurf项目 网站能检查到吗"}],"timestamp":1776343621195}}
{"type":"message","id":"6df8b102","parentId":"ebc582b3","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:47:13.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether VibeSurf (the previous browser automation tool they mentioned earlier) can also be detected by websites. Let me think about this...\n\nVibeSurf is a browser automation tool. It likely uses Playwright or similar technology under the hood. The detection principles are the same as any browser automation tool - websites can detect the automation signatures like navigator.webdriver, missing plugins, etc.\n\nSo the answer is similar: yes, websites can potentially detect VibeSurf's automation, just like any other browser automation tool. The detection depends on the implementation details, not specifically on whether there's a visible browser control indicator."},{"type":"text","text":"是的，**VibeSurf 同样可以被网站检测到**。\n\n原理一样——VibeSurf 底层也是用 Playwright/CDP 来控制浏览器，网站检测的是**自动化特征**，不是有没有提示。\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n| 工具 | 用户可见提示 | 网站检测 |\n|------|------------|---------|\n| **VibeSurf** | ❌ 无 | ❌ 可检测 |\n| **openclaw 独立实例** | ❌ 无 | ❌ 可检测 |\n| **user profile（你的Chrome）** | ✅ 有 | ❌ 可检测（但特征更少）|\n\n---\n\n## 防检测的关键\n\n不是有没有提示，而是：\n- ✅ 用**真实用户的 Chrome**（user profile）\n- ✅ 避免异常行为（太快、太规律）\n- ✅ 网站登录状态（更像真实用户）\n\n所以用 `user` profile 是目前**最难被检测**的方案 ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776343621203,"responseId":"06300d45dc3f7ead02c13bbe6fe1063f"}}
