{"type":"message","id":"58f0d352","parentId":"f2bb2e5f","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:49:09.170Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 20:49:07 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b5139e2e4e4acc2421321536789c]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5139e2e4e4acc2421321536789c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 20:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n好，我安装一下插件，明天开始测试 两个选品流程，，后面是不是可以直接写成skil更方便"}],"timestamp":1776343749165}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd27cc26","parentId":"58f0d352","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:49:22.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Install the plugin (I think they mean the Chrome extension for echotik or something similar)\n2. Start testing the two selection workflows tomorrow\n3. Eventually write it as a skill for easier automation\n\nThey're asking if we can turn the workflow into a skill later. Yes, absolutely! That's a great idea - we can create a skill that automates the product selection workflow.\n\nLet me confirm they're ready and give them a preview of what we'll do."},{"type":"text","text":"没错！完全可以写成 **Skill**，一劳永逸 ✅\n\n---\n\n## 计划\n\n### 今天（准备工作）\n1. 安装插件\n2. 确保 `user` profile + Chrome 连接正常\n\n### 明天开始测试\n1. 测试选品流程（数据采集 → 初筛 → 利润测算 → 等级判定 → 写入飞书 Bitable）\n2. 根据实际情况调整参数\n\n### 后期封装成 Skill\n把整个流程写成可复用的 Skill，比如：\n- `tiktok-product-selector` — 自动执行选品全流程\n- 一条命令启动：`/select-products --market th,VN --category hair-accessories`\n\n---\n\n## Skill 化后的好处\n\n| | 现在 | Skill 化后 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 执行选品 | 需要一步步指令 | 一条命令搞定 |\n| 定时执行 | 每次手动触发 | 设定 cron 自动跑 |\n| 复用 | 每次重新描述流程 | 标准化输出 |\n| 维护 | 记住每个步骤 | 更新 Skill 就更新流程 |\n\n---\n\n安装好插件后告诉我，明天开始正式测试！ 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776343749170,"responseId":"06300dc5bb4fa0cb3ee6ac4b07511ae6"}}
