{"type":"message","id":"555ad925","parentId":"b6342bdb","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:51:39.276Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 20:51:36 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b5139fb4d34a8c3a1d7f7ede93f3]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5139fb4d34a8c3a1d7f7ede93f3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-16 20:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\nhttps://my.feishu.cn/docx/GTh8di7JvopqcBxIALKcryconUc给你这个文档晚上消化一下，除了工具和里程这里面还有策略。有用的都要放到你的文件里面 搜soul文件吗"}],"timestamp":1776343899269}}
