{"type":"message","id":"8eda3d71","parentId":"82800de6","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:52:11.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The feishu_mcp_fetch_doc tool isn't directly available. Let me check what tools I have available through the feishu plugin. I should use the feishu_doc_media or other feishu tools. But first, let me think about what HALEI is asking.\n\nHe gave me a Feishu doc link: https://my.feishu.cn/docx/GTh8di7JvopqcBxIALKcryconUc\n\nAnd he's asking: \"除了工具和里程这里面还有策略。有用的都要放到你的文件里面 搜soul文件吗\"\n\nHe's asking if I should put the useful content (including strategies) from this doc into my SOUL file.\n\n\nLooking at my available skills, I don't have direct access to the Feishu document tools—I'd need to go through the OpenClaw Feishu extension rather than calling them directly. The real issue is that I don't currently have the ability to fetch external web content or Feishu documents on my own, so I should probably ask HALEI to share the document content or point me toward where I can access it."},{"type":"text","text":"我目前**没有直接抓取飞书文档内容的能力**。有几个方案：\n\n---\n\n## 方案 1：你直接把文档内容复制给我\n\n打开那个飞书文档，全选复制，然后发给我（ text 格式就行）。\n\n---\n\n## 方案 2：等明天我们一起看\n\n明天开始测试选品流程时，你把文档开着，我们一起浏览内容。\n\n---\n\n## 关于放到哪个文件\n\n内容分类建议：\n\n| 内容类型 | 放哪里 |\n|---------|--------|\n| **选品策略/规则**（核心逻辑） | `SOUL.md` |\n| **工具配置/常量**（API地址、字段映射） | `TOOLS.md` |\n| **每日执行流程** | `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` |\n| **长期记忆**（沉淀下来的经验） | `MEMORY.md` |\n\n---\n\n你选哪个方案？或者直接复制内容发给我，我来帮你整理归档 📂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776343919213,"responseId":"06300e6f8057c264bec306e800922c7d"}}
