{"type":"message","id":"7ed4435f","parentId":"8b46df45","timestamp":"2026-04-16T13:03:28.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the profit calculation formula in SOUL.md with the new Vietnam model (rate 3570, platform fees 13%+5%+12%+1%+10%)."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_21vmnptagadp_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/SOUL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## 利润测算公式\n\n### 越南站\n```\n售价 (VND) = (1688采购价CNY + 头程运费CNY) × 3500 × 1.2\n毛利率要求：≥ 20%\n```\n\n### 泰国站\n```\n售价 (THB) = (1688采购价CNY + 头程运费CNY) × 5.0 × 1.25\n毛利率要求：≥ 25%\n```","newText":"## 利润测算公式\n\n### 越南站（v3.0 更新）\n汇率：3570 VND/USD\n平台费率：佣金13% + 交易费5% + VAT12% + 提现1% + 达人10% = 41% + ¥2固定\n\n```\n售价_RMB = 售价_VND / 3570\n总平台成本 = 售价_RMB × 41% + 2\n真实毛利润 = 售价_RMB - 进货价 - 物流费 - 总平台成本\n真实毛利率 = 真实毛利润 / 售价_RMB\n毛利率要求：≥ 20%（套装款按套装毛利率，应≥40%）\n```\n\n### 泰国站\n```\n售价 (THB) = (1688采购价CNY + 头程运费CNY) × 5.0 × 1.25\n毛利率要求：≥ 25%\n```\n\n### 套装款额外计算\n```\n套装毛利率 = (套装售价 - 单件成本×数量) / 套装售价\n套装价 = 单件价 × 倍率（2件套×1.6-1.8 / 5件套×3.5-4.0 / 礼盒装×5.0-6.0）\n```"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776344596917,"responseId":"063011157265e54775054ca7e2f1c8e3"}}
