{"type":"message","id":"c5332cd6","parentId":"996e703a","timestamp":"2026-04-16T13:03:57.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, let me also update the TOOLS.md with the Vietnam cost model constants."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z4qy1ro6l2ot_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## 利润测算常量\n\n| 参数 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| **越南汇率** | 3500 | USD→VND |\n| **泰国汇率** | 5.0 | CNY→THB |\n| **越南加价系数** | 1.2 | 含平台抽成 |\n| **泰国加价系数** | 1.25 | 含平台抽成 |\n| **越南毛利要求** | ≥20% | |\n| **泰国毛利要求** | ≥25% | |","newText":"## 利润测算常量\n\n### 越南站（v3.0 更新）\n\n| 参数 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| **汇率** | 3570 | VND/USD |\n| **平台佣金** | 13% | 售价(含运费) |\n| **交易手续费** | 5% | 售价(含运费) |\n| **增值税(VAT)** | 12% | 售价(含运费) |\n| **提现手续费** | 1% | 提现金额 |\n| **达人佣金** | 10% | 售价(可选) |\n| **其他费用** | ¥2 CNY | 固定 |\n| **总平台费率** | 41% + ¥2 | 含达人佣金 |\n| **毛利要求** | ≥20% | 单件 |\n| **套装毛利要求** | ≥40% | 套装款 |\n\n### 越南套装定价倍率\n\n| 套装形式 | 倍率 | 示例(单件35,000 VND) |\n|---------|------|---------------------|\n| 2件套装 | ×1.6-1.8 | 56,000-63,000 VND |\n| 5件套装 | ×3.5-4.0 | 122,500-140,000 VND |\n| 节日礼盒装 | ×5.0-6.0 | 175,000-210,000 VND |\n\n### 泰国站\n\n| 参数 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| **汇率** | 5.0 | CNY→THB |\n| **加价系数** | 1.25 | 含平台抽成 |\n| **毛利要求** | ≥25% | |"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776344623394,"responseId":"0630112f52e01339d1a92b511cc81df9"}}
